Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I select C0 to C7 vertebras on the localizer of Page 01
And	I go to Page 06 of Spine MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio butto
And I select 'Focal tumor' from the dropdown menu
And I select 'I describe' box is enabled and automatically selected

When I select 'Charakterisierung II' tab
Then 'Round' radio button is enabled
And 'Lobulated' radio button is enabled
And 'Geographic' radio button is enabled
And 'Broad-based' radio button is enabled
And 'Stalked' radio button is enabled

And 'Ground glass matrix' checkbox is enabled
And 'Septa/Chambered' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fluid level' checkbox is enabled
And 'Calcification' checkbox is enabled
And 'Nidus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Osteoid matrix' checkbox is enabled.
And 'Fat signal' checkbox is enabled

And 'Periosteal reaction ("sun burst")' checkbox is enabled
And 'Codman triangle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cartilage cap' checkbox is enabled
And 'Low signal of the rim (perichondrium over cartilage cap)' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sclerotic margin' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bone marrow edema' checkbox is enabled

And 'Expansive' checkbox is enabled
And 'Osteolytic' checkbox is enabled
And 'Osteoblastic' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sclerotic' checkbox is enabled
And 'Spinal canal infiltration' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pedicle destruction' checkbox is enabled
And 'Infiltration of soft tissue' checkbox is enabled
And 'Infiltration of adjacent Bones' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pathologic fracture' checkbox is enabled
And 'Origin from midline' checkbox is enabled
And 'Interruption End plate' checkbox is enabled

When I click on 'Calcification' checkbox
Then 'Central' checkbox is enabled
And 'Diffuse' checkbox is enabled

When I click on 'Nidus' checkbox
Then 'T2w hyperintense' checkbox is enabled

When I click on 'Calcification' checkbox
Then 'Max. thickness of the cap in mm' input field is enabled
And 'T2w hyperintense' checkbox is enabled

When I click on 'Interruption End plate' checkbox
Then 'Involvement adjacent endplate "Edgren-Vaino-sign"' checkbox is enabled
